#API
   - npm run local for local environment
   - npm run dev for dev environment
   - npm run stg for stage environment
   - npm run prod for prod environment

This will create the server.bundle.js in the root/dist folder.

##Angular code

    - cd to root/app folder
    - npm run build:prod for all the environments

This will create the dist folder under root/app

## to create a zip folder
 
 npm run build at the root folder to invoke gulp task which creates dist.zip in the root/bundle folder.
